#
# ✒ Description:
#     Git ignore patterns for the toolMan ecosystem. The project is pure
#     static HTML/CSS/JS with no build step, so this mostly excludes OS and
#     editor litter, plus tooling artifacts if node_modules ever appears for
#     local testing.
# ==============================================================================

# Node tooling (only ever used ad hoc for testing — never committed)
node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json

# OS litter
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor litter
.vscode/*.local.json
.idea/

# Logs and temp
*.log
*.tmp
